               patchwork, ggthemes, scales,

```{.r .cell-code}
ship_data <- read_csv("data/Ship_Performance_Dataset.csv")
```

## Duplicates Check





::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
duplicate <- ship_data %>% 
  group_by_all() %>% 
  filter(n()>1) %>% 
  ungroup()
  
duplicate
```
